OL,6,FA former soldier is to be prosecuted
OL,7,Ffor the murder of a man in Belfast in
OL,8,F1972, Northern Ireland's Public
OL,9,FProsecution Service has announced.JThe
OL,10,Fex-soldier and three other veterans
OL,11,Fare also facing attempted murder
OL,12,Fcounts related to incidents in the
OL,13,Fsame year, the PPS said.JKnown as
OL,14,FSoldier F - but not connected to the
OL,15,FSoldier F involved in the Bloody
OL,16,FSunday prosecution - he is accused of
OL,17,Fthe murder of Patrick McVeigh, 44, who
OL,18,Fwas shot at the junction of Finaghy
OL,19,FRoad North and Riverdale Park South in
OL,20,Fthe city on May 13 1972.
